This project has pre-commit hooks installed. They run automatically on `git commit`.

If hooks fail:

1. Fix the issues reported
2. Stage the fixes: `git add .`
3. Commit again

To bypass hooks (NOT RECOMMENDED):

```bash
git commit --no-verify
